g.text: Design Dropbox, which is a cloud-based file storage service that allows users to store and share files. It provides a secure and reliable way to store and access files from anywhere
- Users should be able to upload a file from any device
- Users should be able to download a file from any deive
- Users should be able to share a file with other users and view the files shared
- Users can automatically sync files across devices
- The system should be highly available (prioritizing availability over consistency)
- The system should support files as large as 50GB
- The system should be reliable AND reliable
+ Should be able to recover files if they are lost or corrrupted
- System should make upload, download, and sync times as fast as possible (low latency)
uploadS3(pre_signed_url) -> Upload (if neccessary, by chunks) directly to S3 with Requested Pre-signed URL
- Update chunck metadata with completed status
+ Update event bus with change/add events
+ Use sync_cursor to keep track of last
+ Poll the sync_cursor to see if any
